      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance with this 2004 BMW M3. Powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, this chassis features six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a documented VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under load. While the finish shows minor road wear consistent with an enjoyed driver's car, the mechanical synchronization remains sharp, offering the tactile feedback and balanced dynamics the E46 platform is renowned for.",
